{"type": "article", "id": 5291, "title": "Glowpear™ 模块化自浇水城市花园", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-16T08:00:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606152618XZFJ3NqDB0PhaeYr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款名为 Glowpear™ 的模块化自浇水城市花园希望能够小小地改变室外空间或是你的花园。各模块之间既可以组合使用，亦可以独立存在，扮靓空间一角。对于如今拥挤狭窄的城市人居环境来说，Glowpear™ 至少可以稍稍满足你想要拥有一个大花园的心愿，在你的阳台、露台，当然你也可以将其直接搬进你的卧房。当然，Glowpear™ 也不要求你一定要是个园艺高手，内部的自浇水设置免去了你天天惦记着给小花园浇水的烦恼。定价 199 澳元（约合人民币 1010 元），<a href=\"http://www.glowpear.com.au/new-products/urban-garden\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061526155KNFgZG9mxVXU4kJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152616rOGNfuY4XFbUI5zJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6734375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061526163KGVk0qQLPRjYI1e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152617DcThNmV4eLjogIGs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}